00:34:34,599 --> 00:34:36,920
Sorry I didn't tell you
my dad's company...

511
00:34:37,239 --> 00:34:38,800
-was the one from your school.
-Right.

512
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:41,920
-It would have been good to know.
-I'm not like him.

513
00:34:42,599 --> 00:34:44,880
And to be honest,
I think I don't even like him.

514
00:34:45,159 --> 00:34:46,639
But he's done this for you.

515
00:34:47,320 --> 00:34:51,199
Yeah, he's very good at solving problems
by throwing money at them.

516
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:58,000
Wanna dance?

517
00:36:36,480 --> 00:36:37,960
-What?
-What's wrong?

518
00:36:38,079 --> 00:36:39,159
