and that's that.

529
00:37:06,559 --> 00:37:08,480
You want me to hook up
with the Palestinian

530
00:37:08,559 --> 00:37:10,039
who walks around in a turban?

531
00:37:10,119 --> 00:37:11,199
Oh, sweetie...

532
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:15,920
the idea of making a virginal Muslim girl
fall for you doesn't turn you on?

533
00:37:16,679 --> 00:37:19,719
Come on, you woo her, she falls for you,
everybody finds out...

534
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:23,119
That's it! We cut her down to size,
and she can't act all superior.

535
00:37:25,159 --> 00:37:26,679
Not even if I ask you?

536
00:37:27,400 --> 00:37:29,760
Then I'll let you do
whatever you want with me.

537
00:37:31,639 --> 00:37:33,400
I already do whatever I want with you.

538
00:37:34,599 --> 00:37:35,960
Not even half of it.

539
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:45,559
I'm thinking today
would be a good day to do it. Right?

540
00:37:45,639 --> 00:37:48,800
I call the tow truck,
and they don't come for me.

541
00:37:51,800 --> 00:37:52,960
Well, I don't know.

542
00:37:54,480 --> 00:37:55,679
Here? Right now?

543
00:37:57,199 --> 00:37:58,199
And why not?

544
00:37:59,519 --> 00:38:01,840
But if you're not sure,
let's forget about it.

545
00:38:18,159 --> 00:38:19,159
Hey.

546
00:38:20,239 --> 00:38:21,519
-Samuel, right?
-Yes.

547
00:38:22,480 --> 00:38:25,880
What exactly did you mean to write here,
on my front wall?

548
00:38:26,119 --> 00:38:28,320
T-H-I...

549
00:38:28,599 --> 00:38:29,440
S.

550
00:38:29,679 --> 00:38:31,519
"This above all:
to thine own self be true."

551
00:38:31,800 --> 00:38:33,400
-Ah.
-It's a quote from Hamlet.

552
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:36,599
Yes, of course, a quote from Hamlet.
Ingenious.

553
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:37,679
But...

554
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:40,760
I think you wanted to write...

555
00:38:41,039 --> 00:38:42,519
thief, son of a bitch,

556
00:38:42,599 --> 00:38:45,079
or one of those names
the press is calling me lately.

557
00:38:45,159 --> 00:38:48,880
Bring the other scholarship kids,
and we'll take a photo of the four of us.

558
00:38:48,960 --> 00:38:50,840
Shaking hands and smiling.

559
00:38:52,360 --> 00:38:53,199
I don't know.

560
00:38:53,719 --> 00:38:54,639
Come on, man.

561
00:38:54,719 --> 00:38:57,800
What's wrong with taking a photo?
It could be good for everybody.

562
00:38:57,880 --> 00:39:00,679
For the town, for the school,
even for you.

563
00:39:01,039 --> 00:39:03,039
I wouldn't feel comfortable doing it.

564
00:39:04,440 --> 00:39:05,320
It's OK, kid.

565
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:09,280
I'll report your brother tomorrow.
Let's see what happens to his parole.

566
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:12,440
Think about it.

567
00:39:23,639 --> 00:39:24,480
What did he say?

568
00:39:25,599 --> 00:39:27,360
He wants a photo
with the scholarship students.

569
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,840
-Really?
-Yes.

570
00:39:29,440 --> 00:39:32,599
That's why he wanted me to invite you.
His image makeover bullshit.

571
00:39:34,199 --> 00:39:36,199
He doesn't waste an opportunity.

572
00:39:37,639 --> 00:39:39,760
Samuel, don't play along.
You don't have to.

573
00:39:40,039 --> 00:39:41,400
I don't mind doing it.

574
00:39:46,559 --> 00:39:47,400
What's wrong?

575
00:39:48,519 --> 00:39:52,880
Nothing. I don't know.
I thought you were different.

576
00:40:03,920 --> 00:40:04,760
Hello.

577
00:40:48,719 --> 00:40:50,519
COME GET ME?

578
00:40:54,440 --> 00:40:56,559
Come on, we have things to do.

579
00:41:06,519 --> 00:41:08,000
What is this?

580
00:41:10,039 --> 00:41:10,880
Olé.

581
00:41:12,119 --> 00:41:15,079
We have 15 minutes
before they realize I'm not there.

582
00:41:18,159 --> 00:41:19,800
Are you taking your clothes off?

583
00:41:31,559 --> 00:41:34,599
That comes off, too.
But slowly, so I can see you.

584
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:38,559
OK. And you too.

585
00:41:39,280 --> 00:41:40,760
Let's do it at the same time.

586
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:29,800
Like this?

587
00:42:30,840 --> 00:42:32,079
Am I doing it right?

588
00:42:32,199 --> 00:42:33,760
Yes, you're doing fucking great.

589
00:42:41,039 --> 00:42:43,079
HEY, COOL PROFILE

590
00:42:45,920 --> 00:42:47,920
YOURS TOO. WHAT'S UP?

591
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:50,800
BORED. WANT TO MEET?

592
00:42:52,039 --> 00:42:53,920
DO YOU HAVE ANOTHER PHOTO?

593
00:43:02,039 --> 00:43:04,239
I can't believe it.
Explain it to me, please.

594
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:07,920
You knew it was him who ruined our wall,

595
00:43:08,159 --> 00:43:09,960
and you let him in our home?

596
00:43:10,199 --> 00:43:11,039
Who?

597
00:43:11,119 --> 00:43:13,159
The skinny kid.

598
00:43:13,280 --> 00:43:16,119
Because he had ulterior motives.
He wanted a picture with him.

599
00:43:17,679 --> 00:43:18,519
What?

600
00:43:19,519 --> 00:43:21,920
Mom, I don't know why you are surprised.

601
00:43:22,239 --> 00:43:25,199
You are the only one
Dad still manages to disappoint.

602
00:43:27,559 --> 00:43:29,360
Those people are poison.
You know it.

603
00:43:29,440 --> 00:43:32,519
Why are you with them every time
I turn around, Marina? Why?

604
00:43:32,599 --> 00:43:33,800
Why don't you leave them alone?

605
00:43:33,880 --> 00:43:36,239
Because I refuse
to let you get hurt again, Marina!

606
00:43:36,320 --> 00:43:38,639
-Pablo did not mean to hurt me!
-Marina!

607
00:43:39,440 --> 00:43:41,280
Now is not the time. Please.

608
00:43:42,920 --> 00:43:46,480
Then when?
Tell me, when is the right time?

609
00:43:47,599 --> 00:43:49,280
Why can't we talk about it?

610
00:43:50,519 --> 00:43:54,320
You've spent a fortune on psychologists
to convince me nothing happened.

611
00:43:54,840 --> 00:43:57,199
That life goes on.
That everything would be fine.

612
00:43:57,760 --> 00:43:58,599
And you know what?

613
00:44:00,880 --> 00:44:04,199
Every time you avoid the subject,
I feel like a piece of shit.

614
00:44:05,920 --> 00:44:08,599
I fell in love with a boy. He infected me.

615
00:44:10,000 --> 00:44:11,440
I need you to say it!

616
00:44:12,360 --> 00:44:13,599
Say it! Say it, Mom!

617
00:44:15,519 --> 00:44:18,079
"My 16-year-old daughter is HIV-positive."

618
00:44:40,000 --> 00:44:41,440
Do you regret tonight?

619
00:44:42,239 --> 00:44:44,800
It was... intense.

620
00:44:45,239 --> 00:44:46,239
But it was good.

621
00:44:47,039 --> 00:44:47,880
You're sure?

622
00:44:48,920 --> 00:44:49,840
Good night.

623
00:44:59,599 --> 00:45:02,239
GOOD NIGHT, GORGEOUS

624
00:45:06,559 --> 00:45:09,039
I love you. I love you more than ever.

625
00:45:25,239 --> 00:45:28,639
You! This is how you thank us
for your scholarship?

626
00:45:28,719 --> 00:45:31,119
-Guzmán!
-By vandalizing other people's property?

627
00:45:31,440 --> 00:45:33,400
-You disgust me!
-What's going on here?

628
00:45:34,079 --> 00:45:34,920
And who are you?

629
00:45:35,000 --> 00:45:37,679
Unbelievable,
the riffraff we have here tonight!

630
00:45:37,760 --> 00:45:39,679
Should I take that as a compliment
or punch you?

631
00:45:39,760 --> 00:45:41,039
Take it as you will.

632
00:45:41,119 --> 00:45:43,360
-Let's go.
-I won't let this prep boy insult us.

633
00:45:43,440 --> 00:45:45,599
I'm not insulting you,
just stating the facts.

634
00:45:45,719 --> 00:45:46,559
One question.

635
00:45:46,639 --> 00:45:49,880
What do you call people who keep millions
that don't belong to them

636
00:45:49,960 --> 00:45:51,880
so they can live the way you do?

637
00:45:52,239 --> 00:45:54,400
Thieves or simply bastards?

638
00:45:55,840 --> 00:45:58,360
How dare you come to this house

639
00:45:58,800 --> 00:46:00,519
to insult me and my family?

640
00:46:00,599 --> 00:46:02,880
Who do you think you are, fucking clown?

641
00:46:03,719 --> 00:46:05,199
-What are you doing?
-OK.

642
00:46:05,280 --> 00:46:06,679
You don't deserve my brother!

643
00:46:06,760 --> 00:46:07,920
Get off me!

644
00:46:08,719 --> 00:46:11,440
Shove your money up your asses!

645
00:46:12,960 --> 00:46:14,400
You! Hey!

646
00:46:14,480 --> 00:46:15,400
You are finished!

647
00:46:15,960 --> 00:46:19,079
Tomorrow, everybody at school
will know you are a fucking criminal!

648
00:46:19,559 --> 00:46:20,840
Forget about your scholarship!

649
00:46:20,920 --> 00:46:22,920
Guzmán. Are you OK?
Did they hurt you?

650
00:46:32,800 --> 00:46:33,880
Does it hurt a lot?

651
00:46:35,480 --> 00:46:36,320
Polo...

652
00:46:36,880 --> 00:46:39,679
Why don't you get lost
and stop making a fool of yourself?

653
00:46:40,119 --> 00:46:40,960
Go!

654
00:46:44,599 --> 00:46:45,440
Guzmán,

655
00:46:46,199 --> 00:46:48,360
don't take it out on Samuel.
He's a good person.

656
00:46:48,960 --> 00:46:51,079
Let's see
what the principal says tomorrow.

657
00:46:51,519 --> 00:46:54,119
Your sister is right.
Samuel is a good person.

658
00:46:54,599 --> 00:46:55,519
Me, not so much.

659
00:46:56,480 --> 00:46:59,960
If you say anything at school,
I'll share what I saw in the shower.

660
00:47:02,320 --> 00:47:03,440
Thanks for inviting me.

661
00:47:07,679 --> 00:47:08,519
Nadia.

662
00:47:08,800 --> 00:47:10,159
Nadia, you win.

663
00:47:11,480 --> 00:47:14,480
I lost my temper.
I won't tell on your friend.

664
00:47:17,000 --> 00:47:21,559
Stay a little longer.
Let me show you we are worth the trouble.

665
00:47:24,760 --> 00:47:26,840
You all are too good
at looking down on people.

666
00:47:27,679 --> 00:47:29,039
Teach me how to look at you.

667
00:47:30,480 --> 00:47:32,000
I promise I'll be a fast learner.

668
00:47:40,199 --> 00:47:41,599
What's going on, honey?

669
00:47:44,840 --> 00:47:47,079
This one needs to be taken down
a peg or two.

670
00:48:08,880 --> 00:48:09,719
Hey.

671
00:48:28,199 --> 00:48:31,440
Are you gonna say nothing all night?
After I stood up for you?

672
00:48:31,519 --> 00:48:34,119
You are clueless.
Do you know what I've done for you?

673
00:48:34,199 --> 00:48:36,599
I had it under control,
and you had to make a mess.

674
00:48:36,679 --> 00:48:38,079
Now I have to clean it up.

675
00:48:38,159 --> 00:48:41,480
I was protecting you, asshole!
Like I have my entire fucking life.

676
00:48:41,559 --> 00:48:42,639
I never asked you to!

677
00:48:42,719 --> 00:48:46,920
Come on, Samu! I won't let those people,
who are a real cancer, laugh at you!

678
00:48:47,039 --> 00:48:50,400
You've been blaming them your whole life.
Maybe you're the cancer.

679
00:49:34,239 --> 00:49:35,559
Is Samuel home?

680
00:49:48,400 --> 00:49:49,360
Is Samuel here?

681
00:49:49,440 --> 00:49:50,440
He's sleeping.

682
00:49:52,519 --> 00:49:54,719
He was up all night hugging the toilet.

683
00:49:55,360 --> 00:49:56,519
He says it's a hangover,

684
00:49:56,599 --> 00:49:59,119
but it's the fear of having to go back
to that school.

685
00:50:01,599 --> 00:50:03,239
He can come back, no problem.

686
00:50:03,320 --> 00:50:05,639
I came to tell him
my brother won't say anything.

687
00:50:06,239 --> 00:50:07,119
Very well.

688
00:50:08,000 --> 00:50:09,360
Anything else?

689
00:50:09,840 --> 00:50:11,920
Coffee, water, beer?

690
00:50:12,320 --> 00:50:13,800
Sit down if you want.

691
00:50:20,079 --> 00:50:21,559
Did you tag my wall?

692
00:50:26,920 --> 00:50:28,280
My letter of introduction.

693
00:50:31,039 --> 00:50:32,559
Next time, finish it.

694
00:50:35,679 --> 00:50:37,480
I liked what you said at the party.

695
00:50:38,000 --> 00:50:41,079
You dared to shout what a lot of us think.
Or at least I do.

696
00:50:41,760 --> 00:50:43,400
Somebody had to say it.

697
00:51:02,800 --> 00:51:04,960
And... is it true you've been to jail?

698
00:51:06,079 --> 00:51:07,880
You love to ask questions, huh?

699
00:51:09,639 --> 00:51:11,159
Yes, but only for a short while.

700
00:51:11,239 --> 00:51:12,960
Sleeping badly, eating worse.

701
00:51:13,039 --> 00:51:16,119
No women,
unless you count my mother, my lawyer,

702
00:51:16,199 --> 00:51:19,079
and my second aunt from Murcia.
I'm not sure why she came.

703
00:51:20,280 --> 00:51:22,199
None like you, I can tell you that.

704
00:51:26,559 --> 00:51:28,360
Stay any longer,
and I'll make you iron.

705
00:51:29,840 --> 00:51:30,679
I'll go.

706
00:51:30,760 --> 00:51:31,599
You'd better.

707
00:51:36,679 --> 00:51:38,639
-Bye.
-Bye.

708
00:52:01,320 --> 00:52:04,440
Here you go. Washed and pressed.
By the way...

709
00:52:04,519 --> 00:52:07,360
fancy girl was here.
She wants you to go back to school.

